yup,already uploaded both books in the "Veteran" series - 

http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/6755810/Fantasy_SciFi_Thriller_Mystery_Horror-_New_Releases_6

The thing is that piratebay search feature is not that good,so if you are looking for something and it's not in the torrent name,it wwill not show up in   search.

The best way to search for stuff is to use google search in the following way,for example - 

thepiratebay Gavin Smith

it shows up as the 3rd result in google search!
